  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to examine the effects of playing video games on various components
      of energy balance and substrate metabolism as well as on glucose homeostasis and relevant
      hormonal systems that might be involved in the underlying mechanisms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
